      • doesMessageContainsInLogEntries

        public static boolean doesMessageContainsInLogEntries(AutomationDriver driver,
                                                      java.lang.String message)
        Will search through logs and search for string param message. If message contains in a LogEntry, returns true. Else false. NOTE: Logs will be consumed as method is called. Subsequent calls will only return new logs gathered since last call.
        Parameters:
        driver - to use and go through log messages with
        message - to search through log entries with.
        Returns:
        true if param 'message' contains in any LogEntry
